  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The DxN Hepatitis B Virus (HBV) Assay is an in vitro diagnostic assay intended as an aid in
      the management of HBV-infected individuals undergoing antiviral therapy. The purpose of the
      study is to establish the clinical performance of the DxN HBV Assay for plasma samples in the
      intended use population.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
